title: Qualcomm Issues Muted Outlook, Signaling Sustained Smartphone Demand Weakness
description: The mobile-phone chip company is diversifying into new areas as its core market slows.

title: How to Store Your Bike Like a Professional
description: Stop leaning your bike against a bookcase. A guide to choosing the best floor racks and bike mounts with recommendations from experts.

title: TikTok Is Launching an Ad Product for Publishers and Giving Them a 50% Cut

description: The Federal Trade Commission proposed barring Meta Platforms from profiting off data it collects from young users, after concluding that the company repeatedly violated its privacy promises.

description: The software company’s move to let go about 600 employees follows a recent string of job cuts in the tech industry and beyond.
